According to the BBC , British singer George Michael died on Sunday at his home in England.&nbsp; The musician - whose career started in the 80's with pop group WHAM! - has had many hits such as Careless Whisper and Faith. Tributes for the star have poured in on social media, from celebrities and non-famous fans alike.&nbsp; http://www.channel24.co.za/Music/News/george-michael-dies-at-53-20161226